
Increment / Decrement Operator (++, --) : It'll increment or decrement the value

++ : Increment value of variables by 1
-- : Decrement the value of variables by 1

Postfix Operator

exp++; operator comes after the variable
first - complete other operators and then increment the value

Prefix Operator

++exp; operator comes before the variable
first - increment the value (++), then make other operators